    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/e8e1ef190f21efe547da15d2ff602222.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/e8e1ef190f21efe547da15d2ff602222.webm?t=1710529611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 兼具复古和现代风格的 Roguelite 冒险游戏，可供单人和双人游玩<br> <br> 刺激的动作冒险，对快速反应和高超战斗技巧的终极考验。在体验精彩故事的旅途中，学习新的技能并不断升级。独自出发或是结伴踏上征程，开启一段奇异的冒险。在这个危机四伏的世界里，眼见不一定为真！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/a2506a0a84f24ca1e8c3b97ea26ae1e9.webp?t=1710529611\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/a2506a0a84f24ca1e8c3b97ea26ae1e9.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=78 /></picture></span><br> 拿起你的曲棍球棍并前往帛空市，找出是谁夺走了你的家！对抗被赋予生命的垃圾桶，和鱼头人交朋友。通过各种升级来改变游玩风格，并击败强大的敌人！一段看似微不足道的儿童玩闹之旅，却会引领他们走入一个出人意料的巨大阴谋。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/b57f9d0b48b371dfad1a134f32474678.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/b57f9d0b48b371dfad1a134f32474678.webm?t=1710529611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/b57f9d0b48b371dfad1a134f32474678.mp4?t=1710529611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/620d34eea3bd8e942376fe186fb8c038.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/620d34eea3bd8e942376fe186fb8c038.webm?t=1710529611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 你来到帛空市，眼前景象已经变得不同。仙人掌拥有了知觉，馅饼也会愤怒，更可怕的是，它们竟然发动了攻击！但并非所有改变都是邪恶的，有些善良的角色似乎也获得了强大的力量。招募并将他们变为可选角色，好好利用他们独特的游玩风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/6614b47b11a88c3d44c6e1405c1e893d.gif?t=1710529611\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/6614b47b11a88c3d44c6e1405c1e893d.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br> 挑战强大的头目，推进故事发展，在不同章节中享受精彩的 roguelite 游戏体验。帮助城内居民，并不断开启新的地点。有些居民甚至会让你加入秘密俱乐部，并且提供他们的力量为你所用。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/1523e6b0b12536e2948edf0143ff270f.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/1523e6b0b12536e2948edf0143ff270f.webm?t=1710529611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/1523e6b0b12536e2948edf0143ff270f.mp4?t=1710529611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/34c688f1fcd84f7596c82b950543fd15.gif?t=1710529611\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/34c688f1fcd84f7596c82b950543fd15.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br> SOULBOUND 支持单人和合作游戏模式。你可以独自面对挑战，也可以和一位小伙伴联手开始冒险。无论是在线还是离线模式，都同样精彩！在使用合作模式时，敌人和头目将会拥有专为双人体验设计的独特能力。<br> <br> <br> <strong>好了，让我们有话直说！</strong><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重点特色</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> 重视反应和技巧的战斗，棒极了！<br> </li><li> 丰富的可选角色，各自拥有独特的游玩风格<br> </li><li> 击败极具挑战性的头目，完成一个个章节并推动故事剧情的发展<br> </li><li> 随着旅程的深入，不断开启新的地点和区域，揭开帛空市的全貌<br> </li><li> 加入俱乐部！赢得居民的信任并获得奖励<br> </li><li> 同时支持离线和在线的单人或双人合作模式<br> </li><li> 结合 2D 和 3D 特点的画风，温馨又引人入胜<br> </li><li> 发掘秘密和隐藏头目<br> </li><li> 一只老鼠<br> </li><li><i>...还不止如此！</i> </li></ul> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/a0629790428c0c5ae7e4d153bf7c030c.apng?t=1710529611\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211130/extras/a0629790428c0c5ae7e4d153bf7c030c.poster.avif?t=1710529611\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=149 /></picture></span>",
